00:25:13.037 --> 00:25:14.461
Will you tell me now?

00:25:14.811 --> 00:25:15.811
Hm?

00:25:16.231 --> 00:25:17.231
What are you thinking?

00:25:17.981 --> 00:25:19.981
Ever since you broke up with your ex,

00:25:21.011 --> 00:25:22.381
you’ve never dated anyone?

00:25:22.681 --> 00:25:23.349
That’s right.

00:25:23.589 --> 00:25:26.261
Whoa, that’s a long time.

00:25:26.751 --> 00:25:28.647
How did you manage to stay single
until I came along?

00:25:28.671 --> 00:25:31.861
Why? Are you saying I’m that good?

00:25:41.241 --> 00:25:44.861
Someone this good
belongs to you, Mr. Inthu.

00:25:54.441 --> 00:25:59.085
Does that mean…

00:25:59.991 --> 00:26:01.325
you accept me as your boyfriend?

00:26:04.571 --> 00:26:06.131
Are you a doctor or a badminton player?

00:26:06.711 --> 00:26:08.351
You never miss when you drop those lines.

00:26:09.521 --> 00:26:10.869
Is that a yes?

00:26:16.131 --> 00:26:17.131
Not yet.

00:26:17.321 --> 00:26:18.321
You have to wait.

00:26:22.661 --> 00:26:25.277
And how long do I have to wait?

00:26:26.241 --> 00:26:27.685
I don’t know that either.

00:26:34.531 --> 00:26:36.051
Consider that my way of reserving you.

00:26:40.241 --> 00:26:41.405
You’re not turning away?

00:26:41.931 --> 00:26:43.269
Why would I?

00:26:54.241 --> 00:26:55.733
What are you doing?

00:27:04.911 --> 00:27:06.911
Slow down, Doctor.

00:27:08.931 --> 00:27:10.453
I’m a critical care doctor, In.

00:27:10.921 --> 00:27:12.693
I only give strong treatments.

00:27:13.401 --> 00:27:15.221
Maybe it’s a little too strong?

00:27:16.661 --> 00:27:19.061
Mr. Patient, don’t act like
you know better than your doctor.

00:27:19.751 --> 00:27:21.669
Doctor, please don’t push it.

00:27:22.525 --> 00:27:24.521
You just started hitting on me.

00:27:29.111 --> 00:27:30.261
Don’t be naughty.

00:27:36.161 --> 00:27:37.597
Come on. Let’s dry your hair.

00:28:29.341 --> 00:28:31.397
Are you still mad that I fixed the chair?

00:28:34.341 --> 00:28:35.341
No.

00:28:37.141 --> 00:28:38.597
I’m just wondering if…

00:28:38.831 --> 00:28:39.831
If?

00:28:42.581 --> 00:28:45.221
If you can fix everything else
in this house too.

00:28:46.881 --> 00:28:51.421
Feels like we've met somewhere before

00:28:51.445 --> 00:28:55.757
I never did believe in fate or more

00:28:55.797 --> 00:29:01.117
If tomorrow turns out to be the last

00:29:01.161 --> 00:29:08.629
From you I don't wanna be apart

00:29:08.661 --> 00:29:10.709
I'll say I love you

00:29:10.733 --> 00:29:11.589
Let me help.

00:29:11.605 --> 00:29:15.677
A thousand times if you want me to

00:29:15.701 --> 00:29:20.189
Even if someday we drift apart

00:29:20.229 --> 00:29:26.869
It won't matter more than our two hearts

00:29:26.909 --> 00:29:29.133
If I don't get to love you

00:29:29.165 --> 00:29:33.581
Then I'll let it go, don't want anyone new

00:29:33.613 --> 00:29:38.125
What matters is you, baby

00:29:38.157 --> 00:29:46.157
