00:38:29.951 --> 00:38:32.917
I haven’t had the courage
to revisit that flower garden.

00:38:38.121 --> 00:38:39.121
Well?

00:38:39.841 --> 00:38:41.077
How was my story?

00:38:44.121 --> 00:38:45.245
Not fun, right?

00:39:19.561 --> 00:39:24.613
People here told me
if you have a mole right here, you’re unlucky.

00:39:28.351 --> 00:39:30.965
They said it’s the trace of tears
from your past life.

00:39:41.491 --> 00:39:42.491
Not true.

00:39:44.881 --> 00:39:47.189
It’s the mark of my soulmate.

00:39:48.821 --> 00:39:49.949
And from now on,

00:39:51.397 --> 00:39:53.597
there will never be
any trace of tears right here again.

00:40:15.045 --> 00:40:16.045
Thank you…

00:40:18.671 --> 00:40:20.405
for telling me your story.

00:40:32.149 --> 00:40:33.149
In.

00:40:35.721 --> 00:40:37.677
I checked your storage room.

00:40:37.717 --> 00:40:39.533
You’ve got tons of camping gear.

00:40:39.573 --> 00:40:40.861
Let’s camp out today.

00:40:42.961 --> 00:40:44.461
You’re hiding out for your life.

00:40:44.509 --> 00:40:45.509
Okay.

00:40:47.805 --> 00:40:50.045
Then let’s at least watch the stars tonight.

00:40:52.041 --> 00:40:53.041
Thap.

00:40:58.071 --> 00:40:59.341
Where?

00:41:04.109 --> 00:41:05.109
It’s a secret.

00:41:05.641 --> 00:41:06.641
That’s funny.

00:41:06.871 --> 00:41:08.101
This is my house.

00:41:08.511 --> 00:41:09.661
How can it be a secret?

00:41:12.261 --> 00:41:13.261
Deal?

00:41:16.991 --> 00:41:17.991
Mm.

00:41:18.641 --> 00:41:19.641
Thank you.

