when In was born.)

00:43:56.081 --> 00:43:57.081
Thap.

00:43:57.551 --> 00:43:58.551
Do you like it?

00:44:04.171 --> 00:44:05.557
How did you know?

00:44:18.469 --> 00:44:20.471
If you like someone enough,

00:44:22.117 --> 00:44:23.117
